==========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

You can use cpan to follow dependencies. Type in the distribution main directory:
   cpan .

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 FileHandle
 Getopt::Long
 String::Util
 Test::Deep
 Test::More
 TAP::Harness::JUnit
 XML::Simple
 XML::Writer

